Honey,I know. This must be really difficult for you,and
我知道你一定非常难受…

69
00:04:40,210 --> 00:04:41,840
I'm sorry,am I hurting you?
抱歉，我握痛你了吗？

70
00:04:53,590 --> 00:04:55,720
