我带了乔迁之礼来

71
00:04:55,990 --> 00:04:58,360
Salt, so your life always has flavor.
盐，让你的生活有味

72
00:04:59,090 --> 00:05:01,690
Bread, so you never go hungry.
面包，让你永不饥饿

73
00:05:02,230 --> 00:05:04,890
And a scented candle for the bathroom.
浴室用香精蜡烛

74
00:05:05,170 --> 00:05:06,690
