82
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,930
That's nice.
真有人情味 

83
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,690
Yeah. So, do you want to give me a check?
是啊，所以你想开支票还是…

84
00:05:43,970 --> 00:05:46,440
Not now. You can slip it under my door.
你不必现在给我 你可以塞进我家门口

85
00:05:46,710 --> 00:05:48,400
No,it's not that.
不是那样的

86
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:51,310
I just moved in.
我才刚搬来

87
00:05:52,310 --> 00:05:55,440
Well,the guy's worked here for 25 years.
他在这里工作了25年

88
00:05:55,650 --> 00:05:58,210
Yes,but I've lived here for 25 minutes.
但我才搬进来25分钟

90
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:04,110
Okay,I get it.
好，我懂了

91
00:06:04,490 --> 00:06:09,160
Wait! Look, I'm sorry, it's just I've never even met Howard.
等等，我很抱歉 但我甚至没见过霍华

92
00:06:09,430 --> 00:06:11,800
I mean, I don't know Howard.
我不认识霍华 

93
00:06:12,070 --> 00:06:14,660
Howard's the handyman.
霍华是杂务工人

94
00:06:15,770 --> 00:06:19,600
Yes,but to me,he's just "man."
但对我来说他只是个人

95
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:23,240
Okay. Fine. Whatever.
好，随便

96
00:06:23,510 --> 00:06:25,950
Welcome to the building.
欢迎你搬进来

97
00:06:28,580 --> 00:06:30,640
Can you believe that guy?
真是有够扯的

98
00:06:31,020 --> 00:06:33,250
I really like his glasses.
是啊，我很喜欢他的眼镜

99
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:42,030
So then President Steve told everyone I was a cheapskate...
史提夫主席逢人就说我吝啬 

100
00:06:42,330 --> 00:06:44,300
...and now the whole building hates me.
现在整栋楼的人都讨厌我

101
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:46,990
A little kid spit on my knee.
有小孩朝我的膝盖吐口水

102
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:51,200
