还叫我用百元大钞去擦

103
00:06:52,510 --> 00:06:54,810
You really should wipe it off with something.
你是该擦一下

104
00:06:57,510 --> 00:06:58,500
You know what?
你们猜怎样？

105
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:01,980
I'll throw a party. For everyone in the building.
我要办一场派对 邀请整栋楼的人

106
00:07:02,980 --> 00:07:07,150
And I'll sit them all down and explain that I am not a bad guy.
我要请他们坐下，告诉他们 我不是坏人

107
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:10,190
I am not a cheap guy. I'm just a guy...
不是吝啬 我只是个...

108
00:07:10,460 --> 00:07:12,690
...who stands up for what he believes in.
...坚持理念 

109
00:07:13,030 --> 00:07:15,430
A man with principles.
有原则的人

110
00:07:15,660 --> 00:07:17,430
Sounds like a fun party.
听起来真好玩

111
00:07:19,530 --> 00:07:23,200
If you want them to like you, why don't you just pay the $100?
罗斯，如果你希望邻居喜欢你 为什么不付钱算了？

112
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:25,170
The party will cost you more.
办一场派对更花钱

113
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:26,670
That doesn't matter!
那不重要

114
00:07:27,210 --> 00:07:30,640
It's my principles! We're talking about my principles!
这是原则问题 重点是我的原则

115
00:07:31,050 --> 00:07:34,280
I thought it was about your neighbors liking you.
好，我以为重点是讨邻居喜欢

116
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:38,350
They'll like me once they come to my awesome party.
等他们参加过我的派对 就会喜欢我了

117
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,950
I gotta get some nametags.
我得走了，我要去买名牌

118
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:49,400
And that crazy party animal will be your brother-in-law.
那个派对动物会是你的大舅子

119
00:07:51,030 --> 00:07:53,500
Very funny. But don't say that to Monica.
真幽默，但别对着摩妮卡讲 

120
00:07:53,730 --> 00:07:55,960
Don't put any ideas in her head.
别让她有那些念头

121
00:07:56,470 --> 00:08:00,910
You do realize that those ideas are probably already in Monica's head?
钱德，你应该知道 她可能本来就有那种念头了

122
00:08:01,580 --> 00:08:03,040
