当然 

135
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:47,120
I'm completely different from Richard.
而且情况完全不同

136
00:08:47,290 --> 00:08:50,520
He's an eye doctor, and I don't wear glasses.
理查是眼科医生 我连眼镜都没戴

137
00:08:53,060 --> 00:08:54,050
You're right.
你说得对

138
00:08:54,430 --> 00:08:58,060
