是你让它变好笑的，是你好笑

144
00:09:24,590 --> 00:09:27,720
Look,Katie. Listen, we need to talk, okay?
凯蒂，我们得沟通一下

145
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:32,020
Look,I like you. I really do. I like you a lot.
